Revision history for Perl module Pod::L10N

1.08 2025-06-08T16:14:46Z

	- upgrade upstream to 1.33 (5.36.0-based)
	- fix test failure on Pod::Simple 3.46 or later

1.07 2022-09-16T09:45:36Z

